    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col">
        <p>Day one brought 13.4 miles of paddling, and believe me, after a
        long day of paddling, it was extremely nice to arrive at camp. Night One
        was stayed at Mee Corner. A very large campground big enough for multiple
        tents. Being that it was just the 2 tents we had plenty of room. Camp
        was awesome. The night brought trains, toads and scenic canyon views.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

