    <!-- Day Three -->
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col">
        <p>Unfortunately the last day of the trip would bring more paddling.
        As we all live in Denver we were eager to get on the river and get moving.
        6 a.m. came too soon. With the sun rising slowly we were up and packing up
        getting ready for the long trip home. This was an eventful day on the
        boats. Once we passed the Utah border the wildlife made itself knows. With
        only a few miles to the car we were lucky enough to see a Bear and Bald
        Eagles. </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

