    <!-- Conclusion -->
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col">
        <p>This was the first of many river trips that will be had for us. It was
        not only a fun trip but the beginning of a new tradition. As backpackers
        we prepared as if we were going on an ultralight trip. Next time we will
        do it like the veterans of the river. Instead of packing light we
        will bring supplies in a little more luxurious way. More cold water and
        burgers would go a long way, and of course, COLD BEERS!</p>
        </div>
